metadata.description: makes n = 8 plates. Each plate is preloaded with 2 compounds (3 wells/ compound), and 2 wells of vinblastine. final volume in wells (except for col 10-12) is 7.5uL volume. Load volume to sample wells is (column 1) is 15ul. Load volume of DMSO (columns 11, 12) is 60ul.
